            "controller_support": "full",
            "detailed_description": "<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/536450/extras/vz_desc.png?t=1542283731\" ><br>Vzerthos is a 2D isometric old-school techno-fantasy styled Top-Down Shooter. Player's arsenal includes skills of the Thunder God's heir and three types of guns - use them to slice and dice, burn and blow up your enemies!<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/536450/extras/vz_plot.png?t=1542283731\" ><br>Hero under the player's control must rescue a kidnapped princess <i>Se'Vera</i> from the evil Baron <i>Vakhzon</i>.<br>Not only the guards of Baron attack <i>Vzerthos</i>, but his ally <i>Messenger</i> took his magical powers by order of the <i>Thunder God</i>.<br>Now the heir should return his power, to break into Vakhzon castle and rescue the princess!<br><strong>(Princess is exactly in this castle!)</strong><br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/536450/extras/vz_feat.png?t=1542283731\" ><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Graphical style<br>\tAccording to the canons of the old school - isometric graphics pre-render low-poly models and hand drawn visuals construct a unique graphical style.<br><br></li><li> Comics-cutscenes<br>\tGame story is told through small and simple comics.<br><br></li><li> Ability to customize the interface for yourself!<br>\tYou can define an individual and user-friendly interface for yourself using a special text file! You can change not only the position of the elements, but also the visual components!<br><br></li><li> Open localization<br>\tIf you notice an error or don't like the translation, you can easily open a text file with localization and replace the text! This will make translation better, or even create a new language for the game!</li></ul>",
            "about_the_game": "<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/536450/extras/vz_desc.png?t=1542283731\" ><br>Vzerthos is a 2D isometric old-school techno-fantasy styled Top-Down Shooter. Player's arsenal includes skills of the Thunder God's heir and three types of guns - use them to slice and dice, burn and blow up your enemies!<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/536450/extras/vz_plot.png?t=1542283731\" ><br>Hero under the player's control must rescue a kidnapped princess <i>Se'Vera</i> from the evil Baron <i>Vakhzon</i>.<br>Not only the guards of Baron attack <i>Vzerthos</i>, but his ally <i>Messenger</i> took his magical powers by order of the <i>Thunder God</i>.<br>Now the heir should return his power, to break into Vakhzon castle and rescue the princess!<br><strong>(Princess is exactly in this castle!)</strong><br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/536450/extras/vz_feat.png?t=1542283731\" ><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Graphical style<br>\tAccording to the canons of the old school - isometric graphics pre-render low-poly models and hand drawn visuals construct a unique graphical style.<br><br></li><li> Comics-cutscenes<br>\tGame story is told through small and simple comics.<br><br></li><li> Ability to customize the interface for yourself!<br>\tYou can define an individual and user-friendly interface for yourself using a special text file! You can change not only the position of the elements, but also the visual components!<br><br></li><li> Open localization<br>\tIf you notice an error or don't like the translation, you can easily open a text file with localization and replace the text! This will make translation better, or even create a new language for the game!</li></ul>",
            "short_description": "Vzerthos is a 2D isometric old-school techno-fantasy styled Top-Down Shooter. Player's arsenal includes skills of the Thunder God's heir and three types of guns - use them to slice and dice, burn and blow up your enemies!",
